name: Marilyn Lange
description:
Marilyn Lange

Playmate of the Month May 1974 and Playmate of the Year 1975.

My teenage crush back in the days. This is my first contribution here.
Trained on V1.5 pruned-emaonly
9000 Steps
Batch size 3
Gradient accumulation steps 2
Using Google Colab with TheLastBen‘s notebook.

I used all the color images of her that I could find in which she didn't wear any "weird" clothing i.e. the wet blouse she wears on some photos.

The sample images were generated with the epicDiffusion Model.
